{"id": "1366690241443790921", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢\n歡迎來到克萊門汀醫生的私人神經療養院，請跟隨醫生的指引，釋放你心靈所有的痛苦，走向最終的痊癒。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Dream of Psychedelic Worm Nest》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Dream of Psychedelic Worm Nest》 \nWelcome to Dr. Clementine's private neurological sanatorium. Please follow the doctor's instructions to release all the pain in your heart and move towards ultimate recovery.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:19:05.437000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690242299564052", "filename": "OST-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1389732, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690242299564052/OST-.jpg?ex=69ccd4f9&is=69cb8379&hm=04b02e5282f51f40fa411d2f17ad57c0ee781ed8af15a06228d3eb9e571bcedd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366690429726101594", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.心靈密林-The Mind-Tangle Grove-**\n\n不必言語，當你來到這裡，便會獲得最真誠的幫助。\n那個微笑的引路人已向你伸出手，她將帶你走入你自己也不曾看清的、心靈密林的深處。\nYou need not speak. The moment you arrive, the truest aid will find you.\nA smiling guide has extended her hand—she will lead you into the thickets of your own soul, deeper than you have ever dared to see.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:19:50.327000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690429331832933", "filename": "1.-The_Mind-Tangle_Grove-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 46169372, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690429331832933/1.-The_Mind-Tangle_Grove-.wav?ex=69ccd526&is=69cb83a6&hm=71590312740f30bc15bc82808cbaa9ab9be5750ccc85b4a6f9f7551503a10837&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366690665655697439", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.我將行至-I Tread What Must Be-**\n\n\"在那濃鬱不可見日的迷霧中，我將獨身踏向未知的前路。\n我從那霧中撈起塵土、鮮血與火焰，平息那些孤獨的、茫然的、愁怨的淚水。\n我將不再懼怕，只因永恆的太陽早已高懸於我的心間。\nWithin the dense, sunless fog, I walk alone toward an unknown road.\nFrom that mist I gathered dust, blood, and flame—and with them, quieted the tears of the lonely, the lost, the grief-stricken.\nYet I walk unafraid, for the eternal sun watches over me still.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:20:46.577000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690665328676905", "filename": "2._-I_Tread_What_Must_Be-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 50312104, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690665328676905/2._-I_Tread_What_Must_Be-.wav?ex=69ccd55e&is=69cb83de&hm=e2d885129277c5da36aae059e164fdb2f03746e9be9d3309b8eab8b9a771cf27&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366690765849493589", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.默哀-Silent Mourning-**\n\n我們脫下禮帽，向那些故去的、英勇的、偉大的以及渺小的，我們的朋友，致以最深切的哀傷與敬意。\nWe doff our hats for our dearest friends: the fallen, the brave, the grand and the small. To them, we offer our deepest sorrow and our highest respect.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:21:10.465000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690765723402260", "filename": "3._-Silent_Mourning-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 42300310, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690765723402260/3._-Silent_Mourning-.wav?ex=69ccd576&is=69cb83f6&hm=a99a52ccbd337921db70d48171a22acc0b03dde5cad8820926ff3cc3ecfa84b6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366690859013115904", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.億萬蟲鳴-Million Wings Whisper-**\n\n你聽到某人在你耳邊不斷輕柔地絮語，唇齒間的呢喃沙沙作響。\n你仔細聆聽，試著分辨那模糊的言語，直到同樣的沙沙聲在耳膜內側的顱中響起，你才意識到，那是億萬隻蟲類的翅膀在一同密集共振的聲音——嘩啦，嘩啦啦，回家，回家。\nA whisper coils at your ear, murmuring in endless hush.\nYou strain to catch the words—but when the same sound begins to echo from within your skull, you realize: it is the wings of a million insects beating in perfect, intimate harmony: Fzzzt—fzzzz—come home", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:21:32.677000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690858514251929", "filename": "4.-Million_Wings_Whisper-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 51965944, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690858514251929/4.-Million_Wings_Whisper-.wav?ex=69ccd58c&is=69cb840c&hm=2a86720bd424b39f59217b103f73593a246ede922ab6dac9b240edcee6750107&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366690937270440026", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.我心所向-The Pull Within-**\n\n抓住我的手吧，接過記憶中那朵永不褪色的花。\n不要回頭地前進吧，因我們最終一定會抵達，那閃耀銀光的門扉啊。\nTake my hand. Accept the flower that never withers, plucked from memory.\nDo not look back. We will arrive at last, before the shining silver gateway.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:21:51.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366690936721113168", "filename": "5.-The_Pull_Within-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 10355564, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366690936721113168/5.-The_Pull_Within-.mp3?ex=69ccd59f&is=69cb841f&hm=84aff3658b2d0bd76ddd8accc8c4f7074e069f641dd1a5a09f78d000295d42fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366691033877844049", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.灰燼臆想-Ashen Conjecture-**\n\n該如何欺騙自己，才能於熄滅的餘燼中幻想生命仍在延續。\n她沉眠於漆黑的蛹與黏稠的紅，在夢境中凝望遙遠的星空。\n“那太冷了，但我曾經的溫暖又在哪裡呢？”\nWhat lies must one tell oneself to believe life still burns beneath a bed of dying embers?\nShe slumbers in black cocoon and viscous red, gazing through dreams at distant constellations.\n“It’s so cold,” she mumbles, “but where did my warmth go?”", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:22:14.368000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366691033726976111", "filename": "6.-Ashen_Conjecture-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 8864684, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366691033726976111/6.-Ashen_Conjecture-.mp3?ex=69ccd5b6&is=69cb8436&hm=7b4b48a95e130cac86274eb9fc6966f8b7a97806b22c789fcf78ed5ff0efc19a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366691130506481717", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.黏性墓碑-Viscid Gravestones-**\n\n那是一座座活著的墓碑，每顆卵鞘上都刻著他們的墓誌銘。\n他們滿懷希望，崇敬地走入那緊鄰的墳墓。\nThese gravestones breathe. Each egg bears an epitaph.\nWith hope in their eyes, they stepped reverently into the tightly clustered chambers.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:22:37.406000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366691130325860435", "filename": "7.-Viscid_Gravestones-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 27156508, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366691130325860435/7.-Viscid_Gravestones-.wav?ex=69ccd5cd&is=69cb844d&hm=630ed3e960fb9738195d6aafb018c70004991c8d4aa361f2fb4f4c4e04965cd6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366691214094503936", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08.破蛹-The Husk Breaks-**\n\n你於深淵中沉沒，從你的口袋裡，飛出她最後的留言。於是你在無盡的黑暗裡，得見一剎的光明。\nYou sank into the abyss. From your pocket fluttered her final message—and in the infinite dark, a single flicker of light revealed itself.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:22:57.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366691213763285022", "filename": "8._-The_Husk_Breaks-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 29765992, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366691213763285022/8._-The_Husk_Breaks-.wav?ex=69ccd5e1&is=69cb8461&hm=8a2226b1dc7c89f0808ea691c5f114e4add75c4f7f24d93254ea8807158768b4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366691268297625610", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09.集群意志-Hive Will-**\n\n你與之戰鬥的，是無數個同心同體的靈魂。他們抗拒你、他們邀請你，放下無謂的自我吧，讓你無知的大腦，一同加入永不孤獨的集體。\nYour enemy is not one but many. A chorus of linked souls, pulling, resisting, beckoning. Lay down your useless self. Let your blind, stubborn mind join the collective that has nevernown lonlonness.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:23:10.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✋", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "😐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🤚", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1366691267744108564", "filename": "9._-Hive_Will-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 18181484, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366691267744108564/9._-Hive_Will-.mp3?ex=69ccd5ee&is=69cb846e&hm=8ed4d8eb17ed9bb40b93d08410565555f5a14a9efe7e2c96a693480a69559fe5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1366691325595877418", "channel_id": "1366690241443790921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10.不變的抉擇-Choice That Holds-**\n\n曾在你身前的，如今在你身後。\n你始終相信，在你全力奔跑後，在那時空盡頭等待的，一定是那雙熟悉的、溫暖的手。\nWho once stood before you now follows behind.\nStill, you believe: if you run with all you are, then waiting at the end of time itself will be those familiar, warm hands.", "timestamp": "2025-04-29T08:23:23.919000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1366691325256142868", "filename": "10._-Choice_That_Holds-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 8558444, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366690241443790921/1366691325256142868/10._-Choice_That_Holds-.mp3?ex=69ccd5fb&is=69cb847b&hm=115b51d4408b06f5f8ae52380475a8652da7d8994ba05d1d373d3d47a0af2421&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366690241443790921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：迷幻蟲巢之夢", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
